aptain black little cigars and bugler rollyourown tobacco santa fe natural tobacco company inc manufactures natural american spirit cigarettes and other additivefree tobacco products rj reynolds global products inc manufactures sells and distributes americanblend cigarettes and other tobacco products to a variety of customers worldwide copies of rais news releases annual reports sec filings and other financial materials are available at wwwreynoldsamericancom quick links highlighted information and reports sustainability report latest quarterly reports investor faqs email alerts nyse rai    volume  min  minute delay   pm parent company of rj reynolds tobacco company santa fe natural tobacco company inc american snuff company llc niconovum usa inc niconovum ab rj reynolds vapor company shareholder tools latest quarterly earnings latest annual filings email alert registration investor resources securities history direct stock purchase rss feeds contact us corporate investors media rai board of directors sustainability member of contact us email alerts investor faqs eeoaa policy  privacy statements site map reynolds american inc all rights reserved john j zillmer  executive bio compensation history and contacts  equilar atlas   log in  sign up x   as featured in john j zillmer board member at ecolab inc view full profile are you john j zillmer claim your profile   sign up for equilar atlas and view john j zillmers full profile with equilar atlas you can identify corporate executives in john j zillmers network and community follow changes in john j zillmers employment and moneyinmotion connect with john j zillmer through your network of contacts john j zillmers executive work history current board member performance food group company board member ecolab inc board member reynolds american inc board member csx past to view john j zillmers complete executive work history sign up now education mba northwestern university age      john j zillmers biography biographical info